**T5.5** Test `AuthModeType` constants\n113:   - Verify `AuthModePicoD == \"picod\"`\n114:   - Verify `AuthModeNone == \"none\"`\n115:   - Verify: `grep -q \"TestAuthModeTypeConstants\" pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types_test.go`\n116: \n117: - [x] **T5.6** Test `CodeInterpreterKind` constants\n118:   - Verify `CodeInterpreterKind == \"CodeInterpreter\"`\n119:   - Verify `CodeInterpreterListKind == \"CodeInterpreterList\"`\n120:   - Verify: `grep -q \"CodeInterpreterKind\" pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types_test.go`\n121: \n122: - [x] **T5.7** Test JSON serialization/deserialization\n123:   - Verify camelCase JSON tags: `ports`, `template`, `sessionTimeout`, `maxSessionDuration`, `warmPoolSize`, `authMode`\n124:   - Verify round-trip marshal/unmarshal\n125:   - Verify: `grep -q '\"ports\", \"template\", \"sessionTimeout\"' pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types_test.go`\n126: \n127: ### Phase 6: Validation & Quality\n128: \n129: - [x] **T6.1** Verify JSON tags use camelCase\n130:   - Check all fields in `CodeInterpreterSpec` use camelCase\n131:   - Check all fields in `CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate` use camelCase\n132:   - Verify: `grep -E 'json:\"[a-z]' pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go`\n133: \n134: - [x] **T6.2** Verify kubebuilder markers present\n135:   - `+kubebuilder:validation:Required` on Template\n136:   - `+kubebuilder:default=\"15m\"` on SessionTimeout\n137:   - `+kubebuilder:default=\"8h\"` on MaxSessionDuration\n138:   - `+kubebuilder:default=picod` on AuthMode\n139:   - `+kubebuilder:validation:Enum=picod;none` on AuthMode\n140:   - Verify: `grep -q \"kubebuilder:validation:Required\" pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go`\n141: \n142: - [x] **T6.3** Verify godoc comments present\n143:   - All exported types have comments\n144:   - All exported fields have comments\n145:   - Verify: `grep -c \"// \" pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go | grep -q \".\"`\n146: \n147: - [x] **T6.4** Verify `go build` succeeds\n148:   - Verify: `go build ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/...`\n149: \n150: - [x] **T6.5** Verify `go test` passes\n151:   - Verify: `go test ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/... -v`\n152: \n153: ---\n154: \n155: ## Task Dependencies\n156: \n157: ```\n158: T1.1 ──→ T1.2 ──→ T1.3 ──→ T1.4 ──→ T1.5\n159:           │                      │\n160:           ↓                      ↓\n161:         T2.1                    T3.1\n162:           │                      │\n163:           └──────────┬───────────┘\n164:                      ↓\n165:                    T4.1 ──→ T4.2\n166:                      │\n167:                      ↓\n168:         T5.1 ──→ T5.2 ──→ T5.3 ──→ T5.4 ──→ T5.5 ──→ T5.6 ──→ T5.7\n169:                      │\n170:                      ↓\n171:         T6.1 ──→ T6.2 ──→ T6.3 ──→ T6.4 ──→ T6.5\n172: ```\n173: \n174: ---\n175: \n176: ## Verification Commands\n177: \n178: | Task | Verification Command |\n179: |------|----------------------|\n180: | T1.1 | `grep -q \"type CodeInterpreter struct\" pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go` |\n181: | T1.2 | `grep -q \"type CodeInterpreterSpec struct\" pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go` |\n182: | T1.3 | `grep -q \"type CodeInterpreterStatus struct\" pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go` |\n183: | T1.4 | `grep -q \"type CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate struct\" pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go` |\n184: | T1.5 | `grep -q \"type CodeInterpreterList struct\" pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go` |\n185: | T2.1 | `grep -q \"AuthModeType\" pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/shared_types.go` |\n186: | T3.1 | `grep -q \"CodeInterpreterKind\" pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/register.go` |\n187: | T4.1 | `grep -q \"func.*CodeInterpreter.*DeepCopy\" pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/zz_generated.deepcopy.go` |\n188: | T5.1 | `grep -q \"TestCodeInterpreterDeepCopy\" pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types_test.go` |\n189: | T6.4 | `go build ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/...` |\n190: | T6.5 | `go test ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/... -v` |\n191: \n192: ---\n193: \n194: ## Acceptance Criteria\n195: \n196: - [x] CodeInterpreter types defined per design.md specification\n197: - [x] JSON tags use camelCase\n198: - [x] Complete field comments for all exported types\n199: - [x] DeepCopy methods generated and functional\n200: - [x] Unit tests pass with comprehensive coverage\n201: - [x] Kind constants registered in register.go\n202: - [x] AuthModeType enum and constants defined\n203: \n204: ---\n205: \n206: ## Files Modified\n207: \n208: | File | Status |\n209: |------|--------|\n210: | `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go` | Created |\n211: | `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/shared_types.go` | Updated |\n212: | `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/register.go` | Updated |\n213: | `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/zz_generated.deepcopy.go` | Generated |\n214: | `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types_test.go` | Updated |\n215: \n216: ---\n217: \n218: ## Notes\n219: \n220: - All tasks completed at Stage ST-3\n221: - Type definitions follow Kubernetes API conventions\n222: - DeepCopy generated by controller-gen (controller-tools)\n223: - Dependencies on AR-001 shared types (TargetPort, ProtocolType) satisfied\n\n(End of file - total 223 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-002 — CRD CodeInterpreter 类型定义 Tasks\n\n## Metadata\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-002 — CRD CodeInterpreter 类型定义 |\n| Module | `pkg/apis` |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | S |\n| Design | [Stage ST-3 completed] |\n\n---\n\n## Task Checklist\n\n### Phase 1: Type Definitions\n\n- [x] **T1.1** Define `CodeInterpreter` struct in `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go`\n  - Markers: `+genclient`, `+kubebuilder:object:root=true`, `+kubebuilder:subresource:status`, `+kubebuilder:resource:scope=Namespaced`, `+kubebuilder:printcolumn:name=\"Age\"`","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-002/tasks.md","time":{"