{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775840572538,"sessionID":"ses_287a93498ffeFhL5U8XVgdSX8y","part":{"id":"prt_d7857fb26001hEGdkk5L6Smxwq","messageID":"msg_d78578fa6001JmJxPwfP523UXR","sessionID":"ses_287a93498ffeFhL5U8XVgdSX8y","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-e14adff945d94984ac22e5d0bcaa6e53","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-003/proposal.md","content":"# AR-003 — CRD 共享类型与常量 Proposal\n\n## Purpose\n\nDefine shared types, constants, and common utilities for CRD type definitions in the `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1` package. These shared elements provide:\n\n1. **Common Type Definitions**: Shared structs used across multiple CRDs (TargetPort, ProtocolType, AuthModeType)\n2. **Label/Annotation Constants**: Standard labels and annotations for sandbox resources\n3. **Condition Types**: Standard condition type constants for status reporting\n4. **Validation Helpers**: Shared validation constants and patterns\n\n## Scope\n\n### In Scope\n\n| Deliverable | Description |\n|-------------|-------------|\n| `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/shared_types.go` | Shared type definitions (TargetPort, ProtocolType, AuthModeType) |\n| Label/Annotation constants | Standard labels/annotations for sandbox lifecycle |\n| Condition type constants | Standard condition types for status reporting |\n| Default value constants | Default timeout/duration constants |\n\n### Type Definitions Required\n\n#### Shared Types (Already Defined)\n\n- `TargetPort`: Port configuration with pathPrefix, name, port, protocol\n- `ProtocolType`: Enum for HTTP/HTTPS\n- `AuthModeType`: Enum for picod/none\n\n#### Constants to Define\n\n- **Label Constants**: Sandbox owner labels, runtime type labels\n- **Annotation Constants**: Session tracking, authentication annotations\n- **Condition Types**: Ready, Available, Progressing, Degraded\n- **Default Values**: Session timeout, max session duration defaults\n\n### Out of Scope\n\n- Controller implementation (`pkg/controllers/`)\n- Webhook validation logic\n- CRD YAML generation (handled by `make gen-crd`)\n- client-go code generation (handled by `make gen-client`)\n- AgentRuntime CRD (AR-001)\n- CodeInterpreter CRD (AR-002)\n\n## Impact Analysis\n\n### Upstream Dependencies\n\n| Dependency | Impact |\n|------------|--------|\n| `k8s.io/apimachinery` | Required for metav1.Condition type constants |\n\n### Downstream Consumers\n\n| Consumer | Usage |\n|----------|-------|\n| AR-001 AgentRuntime | Uses TargetPort, ProtocolType |\n| AR-002 CodeInterpreter | Uses TargetPort, ProtocolType, AuthModeType |\n| Workload Manager | Uses label/annotation constants |\n| Router | Uses condition type constants for status checks |\n\n## Alternatives Considered\n\n| Alternative | Pros | Cons | Decision |\n|-------------|------|------|----------|\n| **Inline constants per CRD** | Localized definition | Duplication, inconsistency | Rejected |\n| **Separate constants package** | Decoupled constants | Import complexity | Rejected - keep in shared_types.go |\n| **Generated constants** | Automated consistency | Over-engineering for S-size | Rejected |\n\n## Risks\n\n| Risk | Mitigation |\n|------|------------|\n| Constant naming conflicts | Use package prefix pattern |\n| Breaking constant changes | Document stability expectations |\n| Condition type proliferation | Define minimal set initially |\n\n## Implementation Notes\n\n1. **Naming Convention**: Use `LabelKey*`, `AnnotationKey*`, `ConditionType*` patterns\n2. **Documentation**: Add godoc comments for all constants\n3. **Location**: All constants in `shared_types.go` for easy discovery\n4. **Stability**: Mark constants with stability expectations\n\n## References\n\n- Kubernetes API Conventions: https://git.k8s.io/community/contributors/devel/sig-architecture/api-conventions.md\n- Kubebuilder Book: https://book.kubebuilder.io/\n- AR-001 Design: `changes/AR-001/design.md`\n- AR-002 Design: `changes/AR-002/design.md`"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/shared_types.go":[]},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-003/proposal.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-003/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775840572518,"end":1775840572536}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775840572540,"sessionID":"ses_287a93498ffeFhL5U8XVgdSX8y","part":{"id":"prt_d78581d85001LPHUFq60e4ToKb","messageID":"msg_d78578fa6001JmJxPwfP523UXR","sessionID":"ses_287a93498ffeFhL5U8XVgdSX8y","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-39c1871adf824f9383a4440cae05b714","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-003/spec.md","content":"# AR-003 — CRD 共享类型与常量\n\n## Metadata\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-003 — CRD 共享类型与常量 |\n| Module | `pkg/apis` |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | S |\n| Stage | ST-0 |\n\n## Scope\n\n定义 CRD 共享类型和常量，包括:\n- `TargetPort` 类型（端口配置）\n- `ProtocolType` 枚举（HTTP/HTTPS）\n- `AuthModeType` 枚举（picod/none）\n- Label/Annotation 常量\n- Condition Type 常量\n- 默认值常量\n\n## Out of Scope\n\n- Controller 实现\n- Webhook 验证逻辑\n- CRD YAML 生成\n- client-go 代码生成\n\n## Dependencies\n\n无外部依赖，为 AR-001、AR-002 提供共享类型。\n\n## Deliverables\n\n| File | Description |\n|------|-------------|\n| `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/shared_types.go` | 共享类型和常量定义 |\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n- [ ] 共享类型定义符合 Kubernetes API conventions\n- [ ] 常量命名遵循统一命名规范\n- [ ] 包含完整的 godoc 注释\n- [ ] 通过 `go vet` 和 `golangci-lint`\n- [ ] Enum 验证标记正确\n\n## References\n\n- Kubernetes API Conventions: https://git.k8s.io/community/contributors/devel/sig-architecture/api-conventions.md\n- AR-001 Design: `changes/AR-001/design.md`\n- AR-002 Design: `changes/AR-002/design.md`"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/shared_types.go":[]},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-003/spec.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-003/spec.md","time":{"start":1775840572522,"end":1775840572539}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775840572541,"sessionID":"ses_287a93498ffeFhL5U8XVgdSX8y","part":{"id":"prt_d785856be0013BCCBb52yxYEDP","messageID":"msg_d78578fa6001JmJxPwfP523UXR","sessionID":"ses_287a93498ffeFhL5U8XVgdSX8y","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-455c02c04699427fb7a0714aa7266bc9","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-003/design.md","content":"# AR-003 — CRD 共享类型与常量 Design\n\n## Overview\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-003 — CRD 共享类型与常量 |\n| Module | `pkg/apis` |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | S |\n| Stage | ST-1 |\n\n定义 CRD 共享类型和常量，供 AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter CRD 使用。API group: `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`。\n\n## Design\n\n<!-- TODO: Fill in design details at Stage ST-1 -->\n\n### Architecture\n\n共享类型和常量定义遵循 Kubernetes API conventions：\n- 类型定义使用 `kubebuilder` markers 生成 OpenAPI schema\n- 常量使用统一命名规范（LabelKey*, AnnotationKey*, ConditionType*）\n- 默认值常量供 controller 使用\n\n### Dependencies\n\n| Package | Purpose |\n|---------|---------|\n| (无外部依赖) | 共享类型为基础定义 |\n\n### Controller-gen Markers\n\n| Marker | Applied to | Purpose |\n|--------|------------|---------|\n| `+kubebuilder:validation:Enum` | ProtocolType, AuthModeType | 枚举验证 |\n| `+kubebuilder:default` | TargetPort.Protocol | 默认值 |\n\n## Data Structures\n\n<!-- TODO: Fill in data structure details at Stage ST-1 -->\n\n### Shared Types\n\n```go\n// ProtocolType defines the protocol for a target port.\ntype ProtocolType string\n\nconst (\n    ProtocolTypeHTTP  ProtocolType = \"HTTP\"\n    ProtocolTypeHTTPS ProtocolType = \"HTTPS\"\n)\n\n// AuthModeType defines the authentication mode for a CodeInterpreter.\ntype AuthModeType string\n\nconst (\n    AuthModePicoD AuthModeType = \"picod\"\n    AuthModeNone  AuthModeType = \"none\"\n)\n\n// TargetPort defines a network port configuration for exposing sandbox services.\ntype TargetPort struct {\n    PathPrefix string `json:\"pathPrefix,omitempty\"`\n    Name       string `json:\"name,omitempty\"`\n    Port       uint32 `json:\"port\"`\n    Protocol   ProtocolType `json:\"protocol\"`\n}\n```\n\n### Constants (To Be Defined)\n\n<!-- TODO: Define specific constants at Stage ST-1 -->\n\n- Label Constants\n- Annotation Constants\n- Condition Type Constants\n- Default Value Constants\n\n## Testing Strategy\n\n<!-- TODO: Fill in testing strategy at Stage ST-1 -->\n\n## File Structure\n\n```\npkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/\n  shared_types.go — 共享类型、枚举、常量\n```\n\n## References\n\n- Source: `/tmp/agentcube-ref/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/`\n- AR-001 Design: `changes/AR-001/design.md`\n- AR-002 Design: `changes/AR-002/design.md`"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/shared_types.go":[]},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-003/design.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-003/design.md","time":{"start":1775840572525,"end":1775840572540}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775840572544,"sessionID":"ses_287a93498ffeFhL5U8XVgdSX8y","part":{"id":"prt_d7858b444001JTpDDEPfnDEQBO","messageID":"msg_d78578fa6001JmJxPwfP523UXR","sessionID":"ses_287a93498ffeFhL5U8XVgdSX8y","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-8a2a71df4f57451aaf3e54eda0f0b555","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-003/tasks.md","content":"# AR-003 — CRD 共享类型与常量 Tasks\n\n## Metadata\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-003 — CRD 共享类型与常量 |\n| Module | `pkg/apis` |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | S |\n| Design | [Stage ST-0 - awaiting design] |\n\n---\n\n## Task Checklist\n\n<!-- TODO: Fill in task details after design.md is completed -->\n\n### Phase 1: Shared Type Definitions\n\n- [ ] **T1.1** Define `TargetPort` struct in `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/shared_types.go`\n  - Fields: `PathPrefix`, `Name`, `Port`, `Protocol`\n  - Add kubebuilder validation markers\n  - Verify: `grep -q \"type TargetPort struct\" pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/shared_types.go`\n\n- [ ] **T1.2** Define `ProtocolType` enum\n  - Constants: `ProtocolTypeHTTP`, `ProtocolTypeHTTPS`\n  - Verify: `grep -q \"ProtocolType\" pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/shared_types.go`\n\n- [ ] **T1.3** Define `AuthModeType` enum\n  - Constants: `AuthModePicoD`, `AuthModeNone`\n  - Verify: `grep -q \"AuthModeType\" pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/shared_types.go`\n\n### Phase 2: Constants Definitions\n\n- [ ] **T2.1** Define label constants\n  - Verify: `grep -q \"LabelKey\" pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/shared_types.go`\n\n- [ ] **T2.2** Define annotation constants\n  - Verify: `grep -q \"AnnotationKey\" pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/shared_types.go`\n\n- [ ] **T2.3** Define condition type constants\n  - Verify: `grep -q \"ConditionType\" pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/shared_types.go`\n\n- [ ] **T2.4** Define default value constants\n  - Verify: `grep -q \"Default\" pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/shared_types.go`\n\n### Phase 3: Code Generation\n\n- [ ] **T3.1** Generate DeepCopy methods for `TargetPort`\n  - Verify: `grep -q \"func.*TargetPort.*DeepCopy\" pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/zz_generated.deepcopy.go`\n\n### Phase 4: Unit Tests\n\n- [ ] **T4.1** Test `TargetPort.DeepCopy`\n  - Verify: `grep -q \"TestTargetPortDeepCopy\" pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types_test.go`\n\n- [ ] **T4.2** Test enum constants\n  - Verify: `grep -q \"TestProtocolTypeConstants\" pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types_test.go`\n\n- [ ] **T4.3** Test JSON serialization for `TargetPort`\n  - Verify: `grep -q \"TestTargetPortJSON\" pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types_test.go`\n\n### Phase 5: Validation & Quality\n\n- [ ] **T5.1** Verify JSON tags use camelCase\n  - Verify: `grep -E 'json:\"[a-z]' pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/shared_types.go`\n\n- [ ] **T5.2** Verify godoc comments present\n  - Verify: `grep -c \"// \" pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/shared_types.go`\n\n- [ ] **T5.3** Verify `go build` succeeds\n  - Verify: `go build ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/...`\n\n- [ ] **T5.4** Verify `go test` passes\n  - Verify: `go test ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/... -v`\n\n---\n\n## Task Dependencies\n\n```\nT1.1 → T1.2 → T1.3 → T2.1 → T2.2 → T2.3 → T2.4\n                                    ↓\n                                  T3.1\n                                    ↓\n                         T4.1 → T4.2 → T4.3\n                                    ↓\n                         T5.1 → T5.2 → T5.3 → T5.4\n```\n\n---\n\n## Verification Commands\n\n| Task | Verification Command |\n|------|----------------------|\n| T1.1 | `grep -q \"type TargetPort struct\" pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/shared_types.go` |\n| T1.2 | `grep -q \"ProtocolType\" pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/shared_types.go` |\n| T1.3 | `grep -q \"AuthModeType\" pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/shared_types.go` |\n| T3.1 | `grep -q \"func.*TargetPort.*DeepCopy\" pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/zz_generated.deepcopy.go` |\n| T5.3 | `go build ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/.